9.	Выполнить raw SQL-запрос для получения задач с максимальным количеством комментариев.

max_count = Tasks.objects.annotate(comments_count=Count("comments")).aggregate(max=Max("comments_count"))["max"]

tasks = Tasks.objects.annotate(comments_count=Count("comments")).filter(comments_count=max_count)

преобразуем наши запросы в один raw

tasks = Tasks.objects.raw("""
 SELECT tasks.* ,
       COUNT("comments"."id") AS "comments_count"
    FROM "tasks"
     LEFT OUTER JOIN "comments"
    ON ("tasks"."id" = "comments"."task_id")
 GROUP BY "tasks"."id"
HAVING COUNT("comments"."id") = (
        SELECT MAX("comments_count")
  FROM (
        SELECT COUNT("comments"."id") AS "comments_count"
          FROM "tasks"
          LEFT OUTER JOIN "comments"
            ON ("tasks"."id" = "comments"."task_id")
         GROUP BY "tasks"."id"
       ) subquery
    )
""")

